Package: recycle
Title: Set Hook on Garbage Collection
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Antoine", "Fabri", , "antoine.fabri@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The 'recycle' function lets you call a function of your choice whenever
  garbacge collection is called, with a minimum delta in seconds to limit the frequency.
  This can be done in the current session or in another session in the background and
  might be used for instance for periodic notifications, logs, diagnostics or 
  updates.
